             the pawnbroker, and deposed to by the witness.]</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17770115-1-person52">
                  CHARLES
                   GRUBB
               <interp inst="t17770115-1-person52" type="surname" value="GRUBB"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770115-1-person52" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
