                     <interp inst="t17770115-1-person54" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am servant to Mr. Lane, a pawnbroker: I took in a pair of silver buckles of 
               <persName id="t17770115-1-person55">
                  Ann
                   Bolton
               <interp inst="t17770115-1-person55" type="surname" value="Bolton"></interp>
